Message: Hi there! How can I assist you today? If you have any questions or need help with something specific, feel free to let me know!
The user completes the submission of the form
Hi, I need access to an access token to link to my Redtrack

Sure, I can help with that! To get an access token for linking to RedTrack, you need to follow the API integration guide. Once your token request is approved, you will receive an API key. This key will be used to authenticate your API requests. You can find detailed instructions in this article: [API Integration Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/27680147056397-API-Integration-Guide). If you run into any issues with integration, please contact adsupport@newsbreak.com.
